  <brief_title>Safety And Efficacy Of Ziprasidone In Children And Adolescents With Bipolar I Disorder (Manic Or Mixed) (Protocol A1281196)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Four Week, Double Blind, Placebo Controlled Phase III Trial Evaluating The Efficacy, Safety And Pharmacokinetics Of Flexible Doses Of Oral Ziprasidone In Children And Adolescents With Bipolar I Disorder (Manic Or Mixed)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
