  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if flexibly-dosed ziprasidone is safe and effective
      for the treatment of children and adolescents (ages 10-17) with Bipolar l Disorder (Manic or
      Mixed).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
